	for the utilities.

1998-01-23  Dave Love  <d.love@dl.ac.uk>

	* etags.c (getit, Cobol_paragraphs, Pascal_functions,
	Postscript_functions, prolog_pred, erlang_func, erlang_attribute):
	Always make named tags.
